      <title>里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 宣布采取措施为邮局丑闻受害者开脱罪责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/rishi-sunak-to-announce-steps-to-exonerate-uk-post-office-scandal-victims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士称，英国首相苏纳克最快将于周三宣布措施，加快赔偿并撤销对约 980 名被误判犯有盗窃和虚假会计罪的英国邮局工作人员的定罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/rishi-sunak-to-announce-steps-to-exonerate-uk-post-office-scandal-victims</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 10:54:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克谴责香港对言论自由“冠军”的审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/sunak-condemns-hong-kong-s-trial-of-free-speech-champion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相苏纳克谴责香港对黎智英的审判是“出于政治动机”，这使他成为迄今为止唯一一位参与听证会的世界领导人，这位前媒体大亨可能被判处终身监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/sunak-condemns-hong-kong-s-trial-of-free-speech-champion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 10:17:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰认为 2024 年预算不会受到政治动荡的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/poland-sees-no-risk-to-2024-budget-from-political-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长安杰伊·多曼斯基表示，波兰的政治危机不会影响今年预算在议会的通过。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/poland-sees-no-risk-to-2024-budget-from-political-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 10:12:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>胡塞武装在新的红海袭击中发射导弹和无人机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/houthis-launch-barrage-of-missiles-drones-in-new-red-sea-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[也门胡塞武装对红海船只发动了迄今为止最大规模的导弹和无人机袭击，迫使在关键水道巡逻的美国和英国部队做出反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/houthis-launch-barrage-of-missiles-drones-in-new-red-sea-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 02:55:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前总理纳吉布在皇家赦免状态的黑暗中被监禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/malaysia-set-to-decide-on-najib-s-pardon-plea-this-month-cna</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳吉布·拉扎克的律师表示，他们不知道为被监禁的马来西亚前总理申请皇家赦免的情况，此前有新闻报道称，以国王为首的委员会计划很快召开会议，就他的上诉做出决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/malaysia-set-to-decide-on-najib-s-pardon-plea-this-month-cna</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 00:55:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平提升中国与创纪录国家的关系以对抗美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/xi-elevates-ties-with-record-number-of-nations-to-counter-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平去年与创纪录数量的国家升级了外交关系，寻求团结全球南方，帮助重塑美国领导的世界秩序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/xi-elevates-ties-with-record-number-of-nations-to-counter-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国高级特使表示，北京在台湾问题上没有妥协的余地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/china-envoy-says-beijing-has-no-room-to-compromise-on-taiwan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国和中国之间的关系更广泛地显示出稳定的迹象，但在周六台湾总统选举之前，北京和台北之间的言论正在升温。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/china-envoy-says-beijing-has-no-room-to-compromise-on-taiwan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 19:58:12 GMT</pubDate>
